<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5685] Some tests are not really committing when they intend to</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5685</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are some tests that call SolrTestCaseJ4.commit() but don&apos;t really submit the commit command (using assertU() ). This causes the commit to not really run. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
